📌 STAFF GUIDELINES

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

REQUIRED • STAFF ACTION PERMISSION

Staff MUST get permission from a CoreX Team Member before:
• Banning  
• Kicking  

Always include a VALID reason + proof

Failure to follow = Staff Warning / Demotion

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

PUNISHMENT SYSTEM

1 • NSFW / EXPLICIT CONTENT  
→ 1h mute + warn  
Repeat → 6h → 24h  

2 • RACISM  
→ 10m mute + warn  
Repeat → 1h  

3 • DISCRIMINATION / BULLYING  
→ 5h mute + warn  
Severe → 24h  

4 • ADVERTISING / SELF-PROMO  
→ 24h mute + warn  
Repeat → ban  

5 • STAFF DISRESPECT  
→ Verbal warn → 1h → 6h  

6 • LEAKING / SCRIPT THREATS  
→ Instant ban  

7 • ALTS / BYPASSING  
→ Instant ban  

8 • SPAM / FLOODING  
→ Warn → 2h → 12h  

9 • TICKET TROLLING  
→ Warn → close  

10 • RAIDING / NUKING  
→ Instant ban  

11 • DOXING  
→ 5d mute → ban  

12 • ILLEGAL CONTENT  
→ 7d mute  

13 • SCAMS  
→ Instant ban  

14 • THREATS  
→ 24h mute → ban  

15 • LOOPHOLE ABUSE  
→ 1h mute  

16 • BAD USERNAMES  
→ Change + 24h mute  

17 • MASS PING  
→ Warn → 1h mute  

18 • SELF-HARM PROMOTION  
→ 5h mute + escalate  

19 • CHANNEL MISUSE  
→ Warn → 1h mute  

20 • IMPERSONATION  
→ 1d mute → ban  

21 • BOT ACCOUNTS  
→ Instant ban  

22 • DISCORD TOS BREAK  
→ Instant ban  

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

STAFF RESPONSIBILITIES

USE COMMON SENSE  
Judge fairly  

INVESTIGATE FIRST  
• Check context  
• Gather proof  

LOG EVERYTHING  
• Reason  
• Proof  
• Duration  

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

STAFF ABUSE RULES

DO NOT:  
• Abuse commands  
• Punish unfairly  
• Act emotionally  
• Leak staff info  

Violation = Demotion / Removal  

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

STAFF HIERARCHY

• Respect higher staff  
• No public arguments  
• Escalate privately  
• Follow your role  

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

CONFIDENTIALITY

• Keep staff info private  
• Do NOT share logs  

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

ACTIVITY RULE

• Stay active  
• 2 weeks inactive = removal  

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

🔥 SENIOR ADMIN+ PROMOTION GUIDELINES

ONLY Owners / Core Leadership can promote to Senior Admin+

REQUIREMENTS:
• Long-term loyalty  
• Extremely high trust  
• Proven leadership  
• Handles staff team  
• No history of abuse  
• Consistent long-term activity  

EXPECTATIONS:
• Manage staff team  
• Make final decisions  
• Train staff  
• Handle serious situations  
• Protect server reputation  

DO NOT PROMOTE IF:
• Emotional decisions  
• Favoritism  
• Cannot handle pressure  
• Leaks information  

NOTE:
Senior Admin+ is NOT easily given  
Only selected, not applied for  

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

🛡️ MODERATOR EXPECTATIONS

• Moderate chat actively  
• Respond fast  
• Follow rules strictly  
• Ask higher staff if unsure  

LIMITS:
• Cannot ban/kick without permission  
• Cannot abuse power  

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

PROMOTION RULE

Do NOT ask for promotion  
Earn it through:
• Activity  
• Behavior  
• Decisions  

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

STAFF REPORTING

If staff abuses power → Report to Admin+  

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

FINAL RULE

Follow Discord ToS  
https://discord.com/terms  

Act professional. Be fair. Use power responsibly.
